g.text: The system consists of a central control unit, a sensor module, and
a power module housed in a waterproof IP66 enclosure with an
external WiFi antenna. It supports WiFi connectivity and OTA
firmware updates. Measurements include battery voltage,
temperatures (inside and outside), humidity, air pressure, light
intensity, and sound samples, with derived data such as height
estimation from pressure, sound intensity, and frequency
spectrum analysis using STFT. Powered by a 4400mAh lithium
battery with solar panel recharging, it uses a BME280 and
MAX9814 sensor for environmental and audio data. The
